  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Black Mountain, N.C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "May 7, 1952",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "Mr. J. Edgar Hoover",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "c/o U. S. Dept. of Justice",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Washington, D. C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Hoover:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "The motive of this letter is a sincere effort to help avoid",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "useless waste of life, time and money. It is written with full",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "respect to your pressing work, and to the ability of this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "country's scientific experts.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Although your responsibilities may not be directly connected",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "with the intended text of this letter, I sincerely hope that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "you will consider the possibilities, and forward the suggestions",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "to the proper authorities concerned.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "For the past five years the general public has read, and bally-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "hoed newspaper articles related to the \"Flying Saucers\", and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "following the same trend of thought have ignored recent re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "ports made by persons of undisputed experience and intelligence.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "The possibilities of this earth being visited by ships from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "outer space have been lightly suggested by some, while others",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "believe the \"objects\" belong to some nation on this earth.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Granted that some such objects do even belong to this country,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "it is obvious that we, nor any other nation possess and fail",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "to use, in time of war, such useful means as have been re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "ported by the balloon experts connected with General Mills, Inc.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "I am sure that these suggestions will bear scientific inves-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "tigation and that they are entirely probable. Similar to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Columbus and the egg - they may not have been given due con-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "sideration.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "These \"objects\" of undetermined origin (not to be confused",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "with our controlled weather balloons, etc.) are in all prob-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "ability operated by the absorption, compression, and con-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "trolled emission of the sun's energy (basically electricity).",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "As such, they probably carry a potential charge which is past",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "our imagination. An earthly object approaching too close to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "the O.U.O. would have the same effect as grounding a high-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "tension wire, with the total destruction of both objects as",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "a likely result.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "Assuming that some of these objects are from outer space, we",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "would certainly benefit considerably by establishing contact",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "with them, where as, if such a nation as Russia should ac-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "quire this knowledge before us we would certainly suffer as",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "a result",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
